| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5520 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4cfc4195-67d4-5588-9889-0bcd77c9bcc7"
